## ЁЯТб Section 4: Tips for Enumerators

- тЬЕ Ensure only one person is marked as тАЬHeadтАЭ
- тЬЕ Double-check names and relationships before submitting
- тЬЕ Use Bangla labels if respondent prefers native language
- тЬЕ If unsure, ask the respondent who they consider the head

